{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/multiple-identical-options-in-switch-statements","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Vise Istih Opcija u switch Iskazima","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Ako <code>break</code> nedostaje u <code>switch</code> <code>case</code> grani, sledece <code>case</code> grane ce se izvrsavati sve dok se ne naidje na <code>break</code>. Ako vise ulaza ima isti rezultat, mozete ih predstaviti u <code>switch</code> iskazu ovako:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">let result = \"\";\nswitch (val) {\n  case 1:\n  case 2:\n  case 3:\n    result = \"1, 2, or 3\";\n    break;\n  case 4:\n    result = \"4 alone\";\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Slucajevi 1, 2 i 3 daju isti rezultat.</p>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244df","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Napisite <code>switch</code> iskaz koji postavlja <code>answer</code> za sledece opsege:\n<code>1-3</code> - <code>Low</code>\n<code>4-6</code> - <code>Mid</code>\n<code>7-9</code> - <code>High</code></p>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Potrebna je po jedna <code>case</code> grana za svaki broj u opsegu.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18242,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/multiple-identical-options-in-switch-statements"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function sequentialSizes(val) {\n  let answer = \"\";\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n\n\n  // Only change code above this line\n  return answer;\n}\n\nsequentialSizes(1);","head":null,"tail":n